<!-- backend connections -->

1.Step-1 (Install Required Software)
    Node.js
    Visual Studio Code
    MySQL or Microsoft SQL Server
    Postman

2.check node installion
    node -v
    npm -v

3.Setup Backend (Server)
Open terminal inside backend folder
    npm init -y
    npm install express cors mysql2 body-parser nodemon

4.Run Server
    nodemon server.js

5.Paste in Browser (http://localhost:5000) 

6.npm install mysql2 (It allows Node.js to communicate with MySQL.)


<!-- Frontend Connections -->

1.cd frontend
2.npx create-react-app (Rect installation)
3.npm start
4.npm install axios
5.npm install chart.js react-chartjs-2 (to display chart)
6.npm install react-icons